parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the ignition switch can cause the vehicle to stall or fail to start, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle fails to start
the ignition switch catches on fire
the key gets stuck in the ignition
the vehicle stalls while driving
the security and airbag warning lights illuminate.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Turn Signal and Hazard Light Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the turn signals and hazard lights can cause accidents or near-misses due to reduced visibility.
symptoms: The turn signals do not work
the hazard lights do not work
the turn signals work intermittently
the hazard lights fall into the dashboard
the blinker signals only work 5% of the time.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause the vehicle to stall or fail to start, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle fails to start
the engine stalls while driving
the security and airbag warning lights illuminate
the headlights flicker on and off.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the pass lock system can cause the vehicle to fail to start, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle fails to start due to the faulty pass lock system
the pass lock system needs to be replaced.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Intermittent Turn Signal and Hazard Light Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of turn signals and hazard lights can lead to accidents, as other drivers may not be aware of the vehicle's intentions, and the vehicle's operator may inadvertently break traffic laws.
symptoms: Turn signals and hazard lights work intermittently
stop functioning
or only work occasionally
making it difficult or impossible to signal lane changes or indicate hazards to other drivers.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the hazard light button can prevent the driver from activating the hazard lights in emergency situations, which can lead to accidents or increase the risk of being involved in a collision.
symptoms: The hazard light button is stuck or pushed back
making it difficult or impossible to activate the hazard lights.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbags to deploy in a crash can lead to serious injuries or fatalities, as the occupants are not protected from the impact.
symptoms: Airbags fail to deploy in a crash
resulting in injuries or fatalities
airbag warning lights illuminate on the dashboard
airbag housing fails
exposing the airbag.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The unexpected deployment of airbags can cause accidents, injuries, or fatalities, as the driver may lose control of the vehicle.
symptoms: Airbags deploy suddenly and without warning
while driving at low speeds
or when driving over bumps or railroad tracks.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the airbag system can lead to the failure of airbags to deploy in a crash, or the unexpected deployment of airbags, which can cause accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
symptoms: Airbag warning lights illuminate on the dashboard
airbag housing fails
exposing the airbag
airbags fail to deploy in a crash
or airbags deploy suddenly and without warning.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Lack of Disclosure of Recall Information
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure to disclose recall information can lead to vehicle owners being unaware of potential safety issues, which can increase the risk of accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
symptoms: Vehicle owners are not informed of potential recalls
or are not provided with detailed information about the recall.
